23
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,850
Ms. Wen,

24
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,140
where's my dad?

25
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,810
I thought he had come home.

26
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,900
He won't have dinner with us today.

27
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,780
