29
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,100
Should be his university classmates.

30
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,980
Did he solve his winery's problem?

31
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,780
It should be solved.

32
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,370
Le,

33
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,140
