34
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:03,460
You'll do your homework after dinner.

35
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:03,930
Sure.

36
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:04,660
Alright?

37
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,660
Grandma,

38
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:10,250
I'm not going
to the tutoring center again?

39
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,900
You're about to start middle school,

40
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,170
and your schedule will be tight.

41
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,250
Let's stop for now.

42
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,900
