43
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,100
You have me.

44
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,410
I'll give you private lessons at home.

45
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:25,900
So we save the time spent commuting.

46
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,810
More efficient and time-saving.

47
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,100
Exactly.

48
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,250
You have got Ms. Wen.

49
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,340
Right.

50
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:31,900
I'll clean my hands.

51
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:47,020
You're here!

52
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:55,680
We were waiting for you!

53
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,700
Group hug!

54
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,140
Group hug!

55
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:58,900
And me.

56
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,460
Duo, our class beauty.

57
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,340
Can't recognize her?

58
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,370
The gorgeous Duo!

59
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,660
