- Over a decade.
- More than a decade.

62
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,460
Must be around eighteen.

63
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,250
Yeah, about that.

64
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,660
Time flies!

65
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,250
Everyone's here!

66
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,340
Remember?

67
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:13,780
Liu!

68
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:16,580
Right?

69
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,140
Only me?

70
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,250
We were waiting for you.

71
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,140
We were waiting for you.

72
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,460
Sorry, I had some trouble,

73
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,140
but I brought wine.

74
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,370
Yeah. That settles it then.

75
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,040
This is your seat.

76
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,160
Sit down.

77
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,920
Go on, sit first.

78
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:35,250
Sit down.

79
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:41,140
Let's raise our glasses

80
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,850
and do a toast!

81
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,460
We've finally got everyone together.

82
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,700
First, thank three

83
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:51,900
of the Four Golden Flowers

84
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,340
who organized this gathering.

85
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,580
One of them was late.

86
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,460
So sorry.

87
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:55,900
Secondly,

88
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:58,020
thank the Aerospace Academy.

89
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,140
Without our alma mater,

90
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,660
we wouldn't sit together like this,

91
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,250
right?

92
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:02,540
Right.

93
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:02,900
Right?

94
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,340
And last but not least,

95
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:08,020
wish you success
in your respective fields.

96
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,700
How about that?

97
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,140
Come on.

98
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,780
Come on.

99
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,020
Come on.

100
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,020
To our youth! Cheers!

101
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,340
Great!

102
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,220
Cheers!

103
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,900
No rush. Let's drink slowly.

104
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,140
It's been long
since I've had this much fun.

105
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:20,780
Rui,

106
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,460
as a young entrepreneur

107
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,490
