00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,460
Come on.

297
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,220
Feng Rui!

298
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:45,820
To your great success!

299
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,580
Come on.

300
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:52,850
Ting,

301
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:54,730
do you think wine is a good thing?

302
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,890
What else is bothering you?

303
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,370
I don't know what it is.

304
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:06,890
Let me tell you.

305
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,890
Back when I was young,

306
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,850
all I wanted was to be rich.

307
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:13,850
I thought being rich was great,

308
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,850
so I could buy

309
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,770
any trendy bag I wanted,

310
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:18,770
travel wherever I felt like,

311
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,010
and date whoever I pleased.

312
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,130
But now that I'm rich,

313
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:27,100
I suddenly feel life is meaningless.

314
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:30,420
During the years you were abroad,

315
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:34,130
I haven't had a true friend by my side.

316
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,010
Have you thought about working?

317
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,300
What could I do?

318
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,250
Tell me what I can do.

319
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,770
I've gained weight
since I stopped dancing.

320
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,370
Not 5 kg, but 10 kg.

321
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,610
Look, I don't have a degree,

322
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,100
and I'm not skilled at anything.

323
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:57,530
To be a saleswoman again?

324
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:58,730
No way.

325
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:00,010
Over these years,

326
00:14:00,630 --> 00:14:01,890
I've got used to a comfortable life,

327
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,370
so I can't handle any hardship.

328
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,610
Yuan was right about one thing.

329
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:09,890
I'm ambitious but unskilled.

330
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:17,890
Ting,

331
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:19,490
as my good friend,

332
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,490
tell me the truth.

333
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,770
After all these years abroad,

334
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,890
you didn't date a boy?

335
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,700
No.

336
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,890
Not even that?

337
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:32,300
No.

338
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:32,730
Let's drink.

339
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,370
You've got some willpower.

340
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:41,490
Right.

341
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,060
You're

342
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:46,490
a successful artist

343
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,370
and career woman.

344
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,890
But let me tell you,

345
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:51,980
no matter how beautiful you are,

346
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:53,300
how great your figure is,

347
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,460
or how rich you are,

348
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:56,010
if you don't get married

349
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,420
and don't have children,

350
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,610
in the end,

351
00:14:58,630 --> 00:15:00,060
you'll be lonely
and uncared for in old age.

352
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:00,700
Do you know that?

353
00:15:08,550 --> 00:15:09,820
My child didn't die.

354
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,460
Who didn't die?

355
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,610
The child I thought dead

356
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:20,850
12 years ago, is alive.

357
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:23,650
He's been with Feng Rui.

358
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:02,100
Feng Rui, you'll marry soon.

359
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,180
What do you feel?

360
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,340
What's there for me to say?

361
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,060
It's just

362
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:09,100
what all of you've experienced.

363
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,340
That's completely different, okay?

364
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:12,940
Come on.

365
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:15,130
Let those of us

366
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:16,650
who haven't felt happiness

367
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:18,180
in a long time feel your joy.

368
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,340
Wu has been raising

369
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,340
his child alone all these years,

370
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,610
being both a father and a mother.

371
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:28,300
It's been tough.

372
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:29,890
We thought he'd

373
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:31,650
get married and have kids，

374
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,220
but suddenly he became a dad.

375
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,610
Wu,

376
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,490
in this situation,

377
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:37,730
you're leading us.

378
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:39,490
I'm leading you.

379
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:40,940
The leader.

380
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:41,700
Rui,

381
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,820
I've always

382
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:43,980
been curious.

383
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,490
Back then,

384
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:49,060
which beauty was so charming

385
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,460
that she made you

386
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,940
a father in a short time

387
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:55,980
and a single dad?

388
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:56,890
Tell us.

389
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,220
Who was it?

390
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,180
Yeah, spill it!

391
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,370
Who was it?

392
00:17:00,390 --> 00:17:02,730
Hey, don't bring up sensitive things!

393
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:03,890
Liu is right.

394
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,570
But the child's mother

395
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:08,220
is still around.

396
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:09,730
She's back.

397
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,220
Who's back?

398
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,180
How would I know?

399
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:19,380
Well.

400
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:19,730
Look,

401
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:22,620
Feng Rui,

402
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:25,900
let us know when you get married.

403
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:28,010
We're all waiting for that day,

404
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:29,050
aren't we?

405
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:30,900
We're all waiting for it.

406
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:36,660
Let me clink glasses with you.

407
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:37,620
Well.

408
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:38,460
And me.

409
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,050
Let's have a drink.

410
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,660
Come on!

411
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:41,980
You guys...

412
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:42,770
Come on.

413
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:43,420
Alright.

414
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,050
You should drink.

415
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:45,180
Boss,

416
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:46,420
let me ask you.

417
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:47,730
I heard

418
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,380
some news from NASA again.

419
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:50,810
You're right.

420
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:53,050
All these years, I've been all alone.

421
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:54,810
For 12 years,

422
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,980
it was work and more work every day.

423
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,730
You know my father's situation.

424
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:06,980
Not a single piece of news.

425
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,380
To put it bluntly,

426
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:11,460
we don't know if he's alive or not.

427
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:13,250
But when I found out

428
00:18:13,270 --> 00:18:14,660
Le was my son,

429
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:16,620
I felt like

430
00:18:17,510 --> 00:18:18,220
I wasn't alone anymore.

431
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:20,980
I didn't feel so lonely.

432
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,290
I felt my life had

433
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,010
a continuation.

434
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:29,220
But you know what Gao Hui told me?

435
00:18:29,860 --> 00:18:31,180
♪An old dream is like
a sheet of pure white at hand♪

436
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:34,140
When he was three, he got very sick.

437
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,460
He had a fever for a long time.

438
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:38,980
♪Crumpled when held tight,
gone when you expand♪

439
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:40,380
I felt so incredibly sad.

440
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,290
I've missed many moments

441
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,900
when he was suffering like that.

442
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,660
For these 12 years,

443
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,010
mom has always

444
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:55,460
been a void in Le's heart.

445
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,460
He must have asked himself...

446
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,460
countless times

447
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,180
why other kids have a mom,

448
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:02,900
but he doesn't.

449
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:06,730
I hate Gao Hui.

450
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:08,620
From the very beginning,

451
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,290
she stripped me
of my right to be a mother.

452
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,730
I also hate Feng Rui.

453
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,010
All these years...

454
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,660
he deceived me with Gao Hui.

455
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,980
He didn't even call me once.

456
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:28,090
I also hate myself.

457
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,860
I should have seen it

458
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:34,810
with my own eyes back then.

459
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,490
Whether the child was alive or dead,

460
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,620
if I had insisted on seeing him,

461
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,290
would things have been different now?

462
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:47,180
If I tell Le I'm his mother now,

463
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,900
will he hate me?

464
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,770
Siting,

465
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,980
how is the child doing now?

466
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:58,730
He's doing very well.

467
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:03,050
You can tell Le is happy

468
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:03,900
and joyful.

469
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:06,060
Gao Hui and Feng Rui

470
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,740
must be treating him very well.

471
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,100
I believe he's enjoyed

472
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:13,740
plenty of family warmth.

473
00:20:19,980 --> 00:20:20,460
Siting,

474
00:20:22,540 --> 00:20:23,700
don't be too sad.

475
00:20:24,340 --> 00:20:25,740
What matters is that he is doing well.

476
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,940
And have you thought

477
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:29,740
over these years,

478
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:31,420
it's been the best choice

479
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,580
for the child to stay with Rui?

480
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:39,300
♪Who hasn't wondered if their life
would stay blank and bare?♪

481
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:46,580
♪Acting on impulse,
believing futures fair♪

482
00:20:47,060 --> 00:20:48,660
Being with Feng Rui,

483
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:51,260
♪Don't ask how to bury
faults of the past♪

484
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:52,420
all he misses is me,

485
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:54,220
a mother.

486
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,220
♪All my waiting is just to accumulate♪

487
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:58,060
But if he were with me,

488
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:01,340
♪the colors of past and future♪

489
00:21:01,340 --> 00:21:02,380
he'd have had just me.

490
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:04,500
Yes.

491
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:09,020
Do you know?

492
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:12,260
I want to see him every day

493
00:21:12,300 --> 00:21:13,220
at his school gate,

494
00:21:14,580 --> 00:21:16,940
to see which classmates
he's playing with

495
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:20,980
and who his teachers are

496
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:23,820
and to see if he is having a good time
every day.

497
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:26,060
I don't know what I should do

498
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:28,180
to make up for these years.

499
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:30,100
About the absence in his life,

500
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:32,860
what should I do?

501
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,820
♪If we look back,
a lingering warmth stays♪

502
00:21:34,940 --> 00:21:36,020
♪In the dialogue
where time and space part ways♪

503
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:36,460
I think

504
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:38,220
you're doing a great job now.

505
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:38,900
Come on,

506
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:41,020
let's drink.

507
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:42,260
Drink up.

508
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:44,500
All your worries will disappear.

509
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:47,300
♪This posture of steadfast faith♪

510
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:51,100
♪Can't hide the weathering
of wind and rain's wraith♪

511
00:21:51,940 --> 00:21:54,540
♪Let the story settle
in the sea of faces♪

512
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:58,620
♪Only then can the epilogue
leave its traces♪

513
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:01,780
♪The gloom that lies ahead♪

514
00:22:02,780 --> 00:22:05,540
♪The light is shining from behind♪

515
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:09,100
♪Every strand of dancing shadow♪

516
00:22:09,620 --> 00:22:16,700
♪Will weave the days to be♪

517
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:05,860
Peiyan,

518
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:07,940
what are you doing here?

519
00:23:09,980 --> 00:23:10,540
Get in the car.

520
00:23:11,020 --> 00:23:11,700
I'll take you home.

521
00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:14,180
Okay.

522
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:22,820
Be careful.

523
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:43,020
Thanks.

524
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:47,100
Have some water.

525
00:23:49,940 --> 00:23:50,500
Drink more.

526
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:51,540
Thank you.

527
00:24:44,860 --> 00:24:45,940
It's rare to see you like this.

528
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:47,860
You seem pretty drunk today.

529
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:50,820
Anything bothering you?

530
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:52,460
Want to talk about it?

531
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:17,380
Mom,

532
00:25:17,620 --> 00:25:18,060
