536
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:31,980
I've contacted a PR company.

537
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:33,340
They should be here soon.

538
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:35,500
We'll discuss emergency PR measures.

539
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:37,540
If things go on like this,

540
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:38,820
public opinion
will collapse the company.

541
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:44,940
I need to ask

542
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:46,860
for your help.

543
00:25:47,540 --> 00:25:48,220
Tomorrow,

544
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:51,300
go to Melbourne with Mr. Xu
from the International Trade.

545
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:54,540
Visit those suppliers there.

546
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:56,620
We need to know their real intentions.

547
00:25:58,580 --> 00:25:59,580
As you've seen,

548
00:25:59,940 --> 00:26:01,860
the company is in a tough situation.

549
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:03,500
There's no one reliable to send.

550
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:04,780
I'm busy

551
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:05,820
