556
00:26:15,820 --> 00:26:16,660
Don't worry.

557
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:19,180
I'll ask Ms. Ming from our home

558
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:20,540
to take care of her.

559
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:23,140
After all,

560
00:26:23,940 --> 00:26:25,820
she's carrying our family's heir.

561
00:26:26,860 --> 00:26:27,820
I know

562
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:29,540
what to do.

563
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:32,860
At first,

564
00:26:34,180 --> 00:26:35,820
